org.dataconservancy.dcs.util

Class HierarchicalPrettyPrinter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dataconservancy.dcs.util.PrettyPrinter
      • org.dataconservancy.dcs.util.HierarchicalPrettyPrinter

  • public class HierarchicalPrettyPrinter
extends PrettyPrinter
    Provides methods making it easier to pretty-print strings in a hierarchical fashion. Especially where the goal is to present the string form of an instance of the DCS data model.
